DESCRIPTION:Trainer: FRAUKE\nRaum: Kursraum 2\n<p><font size="3"><br/><br/><!--StartFragment--></font></p><p><font size="4"><em><b><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">Drums </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">Alive – </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">60 </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">Minuten </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">Rhythmus &amp\; </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">Fitness</span></b></em><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn"><b> </b></span></font></p><p><font size="3"><br/><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">Drums </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">Alive </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">ist </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">ein </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">energiegeladener </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">Fitnesskurs\, </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">der </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">einfache </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">Trommelrhythmen </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">mit </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">dynamischen </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">Bewegungen </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">verbindet. </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">In </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">diesem </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">60-</span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">minütigen </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">Workout </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">wird </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">mit </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">Drumsticks </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">auf </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">Gymnastikbälle </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">getrommelt </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">und </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">gleichzeitig </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">der </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">ganze </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">Körper </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">aktiviert. </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">Die </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">Kombination </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">aus </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">Musik\, </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">Rhythmus </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">und </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">funktionellen </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">Übungen </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">fördert </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">Ausdauer\, </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">Koordination </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">und </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">Kraft – </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">und </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">macht </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">dabei </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">jede </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">Menge </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">Spaß. &#127926\;</span></font></p><p><font size="3"><br/></font></p><p><font size="3"><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">Der </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">Kurs </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">eignet </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">sich </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">für </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">alle </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">Fitnesslevels\, </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">da </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">die </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">Bewegungen </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">leicht </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">zu </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">erlernen </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">sind </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">und </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">individuell </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">angepasst </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">werden </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">können. </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">Neben </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">dem </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">Training </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">für </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">Herz-</span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">Kreislauf </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">und </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">Muskulatur </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">sorgt </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">Drums </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">Alive </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">auch </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">für </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">Stressabbau </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">und </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">gute </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">Laune.</span></font></p><p><font size="3"><br/></font></p><p><strong><font size="3"><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">Inhalte </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">des </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">Kurses:</span></font></strong></p><ul><font size="3"><br/></font><li><p><font size="3"><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">Rhythmisches </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">Trommeln </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">auf </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">Gymnastikbällen </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">mit </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">Drumsticks </span></font></p></li><li><p><font size="3"><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">Ganzkörper-</span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">Workout </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">für </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">Ausdauer\, </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">Kraft </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">und </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">Koordination</span></font></p></li><li><p><font size="3"><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">Einfache </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">Choreografien </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">zu </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">motivierender </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">Musik</span></font></p></li><li><p><font size="3"><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">Förderung </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">von </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">Konzentration </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">und </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">Rhythmusgefühl</span></font></p></li><li><p><font size="3"><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">Spaß </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">in </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">der </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">Gruppe </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">und </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">effektiver </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">Stressabbau</span></font></p></li></ul><p><font size="3"><br/><strong><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">Level:</span></strong><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn"> </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">Für </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">Anfänger </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">und </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">Fortgeschrittene </span><span class="BZ_Pyq_fadeIn">geeignet</span></font></p><!--EndFragment--><p><br/></p><p><br/></p>
